# Figma-to-code: reuse-first checklist

When translating a Figma design into this repo:

- First map each Figma section to an existing file in `src/sections/*` (prefer editing vs creating new sections).
- Prefer reusing existing components from `src/components/*` before creating new ones.
- If creating a new component is unavoidable, keep it narrowly scoped and reusable.
- Do not introduce a new layout system; preserve existing Tailwind breakpoint patterns and spacing utilities.

## Required callouts in your write-up
- **Reuse** vs **Create** list for components (with paths)
- any new assets required (type + filename + where used)
